DATA SOURCES AND ATTRIBUTION

This project uses real traffic data from the following public sources:

1. Austin Open Data Portal
   - Source: City of Austin Transportation Department
   - License: Public Domain / Open Data
   - URL: https://data.austintexas.gov/

2. Chicago Data Portal
   - Source: City of Chicago
   - License: Public Domain / Open Data
   - URL: https://data.cityofchicago.org/

3. NYC Open Data (when available)
   - Source: New York City Department of Transportation
   - License: Public Domain / Open Data
   - URL: https://opendata.cityofnewyork.us/

4. Seattle Open Data (when available)
   - Source: Seattle Department of Transportation
   - License: Public Domain / Open Data
   - URL: https://data.seattle.gov/

All traffic data used in this project is obtained from public APIs and open
data portals. No proprietary or restricted data is used.

