This software is provided for educational and research purposes. While it uses
real traffic data, the optimization recommendations should be validated by
qualified traffic engineers before implementation in production traffic
management systems.

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any consequences arising
from the use of this software in actual traffic management scenarios.